OL,6,GThe merger of the BBC News Channel and
OL,7,GBBC World News is expected to have a
OL,8,Gsoft launch on 6th March.
OL,10,FBut regular viewers will by now be used
OL,11,Fto seeing programmes in the evenings
OL,12,Fand weekends which are designed for
OL,13,Fviewers around the globe as well as
OL,14,Fthose at home.
OL,16,FIt poses huge editorial dilemmas.
OL,17,FStories of vital importance and
OL,18,Frelevance to UK viewers may be of
OL,19,Flittle interest or significance abroad.
OL,20,FStories of global importance may seem
OL,21,Fdetached from the lives of most people
OL,22,Fin the UK.
OL,3,C"Broadcasting to viewers in the UK and
OL,4,Caround the world, this is BBC News"
