OL,6,FSaturday's combined output gave a good
OL,7,Fexample. The Nigerian election led the
OL,8,Fafternoon output.
OL,10,FObviously the main BBC One bulletin
OL,11,Fincluded a piece from Nigeria but well
OL,12,Fdown the running order. A good example
OL,13,Fof how to bring this kind of foreign
OL,14,Fstory to a mainstream audience.
OL,16,FIt is the kind of story a domestic BBC
OL,17,Foutlet might cover to demonstrate the
OL,18,Fwidth of its international coverage and
OL,19,Fbecause it is worthy of highlighting `
OL,20,Fnot because of its importance or direct
OL,21,Finterest to home viewers.
OL,3,C"Broadcasting to viewers in the UK and
OL,4,Caround the world, this is BBC News"
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G2/5
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
