OL,6,FIt is important for a public service
OL,7,Fbroadcaster to cover these stories and
OL,8,Ftake foreign affairs seriously. There
OL,9,Fare concerns that Africa is reported
OL,10,Fall too rarely except in the context of
OL,11,Ftragedy.
OL,13,FBut a lead story? It is not a foreign
OL,14,Fstory of direct concern to UK viewers
OL,15,Flike the war in Ukraine. Sky News must
OL,16,Fhave been delighted.
OL,3,C"Broadcasting to viewers in the UK and
OL,4,Caround the world, this is BBC News"
OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G3/5
