OL,6,FPerhaps though there is a niche for a
OL,7,Fchannel focused on solid foreign
OL,8,Freporting. Nobody who cares about
OL,9,Fserious international journalism or
OL,10,Fworld affairs would say these stories
OL,11,Fshould not be covered.
OL,13,FThe context in which they appear
OL,14,Fmatters though. Imagine the risk of
OL,15,Flooking aloof and detached from the
OL,16,Fstories so important to licence
OL,17,Fholders.
OL,3,C"Broadcasting to viewers in the UK and
OL,4,Caround the world, this is BBC News"
