OL,6,FIt is unfair to judge the new News
OL,7,FChannel in advance. Yet again, I stress
OL,8,Finternational news matters and not just
OL,9,Fthe foreign news likely to resonate
OL,10,Fdirectly with a UK audience.
OL,12,FBut there must surely be real worries
OL,13,Fover whether the new look channel will
OL,14,Fstill cover a full range of domestic
OL,15,Fstories properly.
OL,17,FThe jury will be out for several weeks.
OL,3,C"Broadcasting to viewers in the UK and
OL,4,Caround the world, this is BBC News"
